messages.title: DEVELOPMENT STRATEGY
messages.content: The SNP's development strategy will put the constituency at the forefront of Scotland's drive for a strong economic recovery and ensure local communities benefit first from the jobs and investment this creates.

messages.title: RENEWABLE ENERGY
messages.content: Investing in Renewable Energy is central to our vision of Scotland's future and central to our plans, helping to drive down our net carbon emissions to zero.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Aims to position the constituency at the center of Scotland's economic recovery by prioritizing local job creation and investment.
Focus on investing in renewable energy to reduce carbon emissions and drive economic growth.

issues.economy: Development strategy focused on strong economic recovery and job creation.
issues.environment: Investment in renewable energy to achieve net-zero carbon emissions.
